dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington. Appears in: A new general atlas, comprising a complete set of maps, representing the grand divisions of the globe, together with the several empires, kingdoms and states in the world. Philadelphia : A. Finley, 1824 through 1831 editions. "55."
